query.statement: SELECT MANDT, CS653_PJT AS PJT, CS653_DAT AS DAT, CS653_SOD AS SOD, CS653_CNT AS CNT, CS653_PAL AS PAL, CS653_JJT AS JJT, CS653_OYT AS OYT, CS653_JGT AS JGT, CS653_BNT AS BNT, CS653_INS AS INS, CS653_RCT AS RCT, CS653_ICT AS ICT, CS653_TOT AS TOT, CS653_ICP AS ICP, CS653_DAN AS DAN, CS653_ORT AS ORT, CS653_SIP AS SIP FROM SAPHEE.ZCST653 WHERE 1=1 AND MANDT = #G_MANDT# AND CS653_PJT = #PJT# AND CS653_DAT = #DAT# WITH UR
